{"tid":688353,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[GDP升]田北辰認為港鐵應考慮沙中綫紅磡站工程是否需要拆卸","createTime":"2018-06-03T06:56:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-03T07:15:55.000Z","uid":51271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c2952e9c378055f766a30db0a1e4b934f3617d40","tid":688353,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T06:56:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1399660-20180603.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1399660-20180603.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=BPmz8HKlJlkZ0v6s2oCfdiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=de854dd5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1399660-20180603.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=988ea411\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1399660-20180603.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n港鐵沙中綫紅磡站地盤擴建工程，被揭發施工出現問題，立法會鐵路事宜小組主席田北辰說，現時港鐵首要澄清的問題，是事件有否涉及外判商造假，港鐵和承辦商是否知情不報。<br />\n<br />\n田北辰又說，港鐵應慎重考慮紅磡站有關工程是否需要拆卸及重新檢測。<br />\n<br />\n至於是否需要立法會引用特權法調查事件，田北辰說不排除這是其中一個方法，但要待港鐵提交報告再作決定。他亦促請政府盡快成立獨立調查委員會，委派專家小組調查事件。"},{"pid":"0685412db5d96f818740c0fa81feff083701a21b","tid":688353,"uid":45332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T07:00:31.000Z","msg":"gdp go go go<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71426f70005e7b6e15e10e4276324d48cabe7778","tid":688353,"uid":26003,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T07:11:25.000Z","msg":"又放多幾百億落去，<br />\n用既錢就嚟夠喺月球起基地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b3132805b77074cc697246dafeff8742aef8a48","tid":688353,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T07:15:35.000Z","msg":"幫手班工人仲賺多筆<img src=\"/assets/face